messages.message:
hey all — could use some help understanding our Fix Versions and also our Release cut dates:
• is 01.19 the next release cut date (primarily for C1)?”
• is 02.04 (for BAML) the release cut date after that?
If so, can we create another Fix Version for 02.04 so we can start pinning tasks to that Release.

cc: @will @georgia chestnuts rust-ing on an open fire @Heymian
The 01.19 should probably get deleted as well. The C1 cut is 01.13. And yup, we should make a new Fix Version for 02.04. I can try to figure out how to do it :D
ya that’d be great — want to make sure I understand the actual code cuts — and make sure our Fix Versions reflect that!
Also @Hari @Nithin — i’m having trouble knowing exactly what you and SC are expecting, and whether it will go in the 0.13 code-cut (this will be tough) — or whether we can plan for the 02.04 code-cut
I also have all the dates kept up to date on the engineering calendar, so hope that helps!
@dlluncor for SC 02.04 cut should be good.
